@Sony has been my greatest ally in sharing our ocean’s story and bringing the solutions that can protect its future to a global audience. They have provided me and my team @SeaLegacy the tools to test the limits of photography and shatter the barriers between people and the last of our planet’s wild places. @SonyAlpha cameras have been my trusted companions beneath the waves for the last 13 years and I am thrilled to help support the launch of the new Sony Alpha 1; the camera that will revolutionize the way we see and document the world. Head over to @SonyAlpha and join me in welcoming this game-changer to the field of photography and the visual arts. With it, we will bring vast audiences closer than ever before to the beauty of our natural world and shine a light on the innovative solutions to our planet’s greatest challenges.
@keshalambert @paulnicklen @jnsilva @charlysavely @phil.yoon @edsel 
